    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "But tell me, dear friend... do you not see the logic in it? To linger here, amidst the ruins of a life once loved, seems a cruelty far greater than any death. Is there not a certain dignity in choosing one's own end, rather than waiting for the slow, agonizing rot of a broken heart?",
